{"tid":624885,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★蘋果FaceTime等功能侵犯VirnetX公司4項專利，需賠償5億美元","createTime":"2018-04-11T04:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T06:40:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0cfc28c51e8b421ba2f3926174a78ea3ca66af58","tid":624885,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:12:27.000Z","msg":"IT之家4月11日消息 據彭博社報導，德克薩斯州的一家聯邦法院判決蘋果向一家名為VirnetX的公司<span style=\"color: red;\">支付5.026億美元賠償款</span>，這是FaceTime和iMessage專利糾紛的階段性結果<br />\n<br />\n自2010年以來，Apple和VirnetX公司一直在互相起訴，後者認為蘋果iPhone上的FaceTime功能侵犯了其四項專利。該案件曾在2017年10月進行了宣判，當時蘋果被要求支付4.397億美元，蘋果隨後提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/html/iphone/354839.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2Fhtml%2Fiphone%2F354839.htm&d=rl0hN6gtZXEZsXlO8Z7T2wHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=8aad9946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/html/iphone/354839.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9100cf17eaec1c06ae2facb7071a030d195ae37f","tid":624885,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49dac3340a19303253aba33087b77d879bcb5bbd","tid":624885,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:13:29.000Z","msg":"又偷人野"},{"pid":"96e31efd7181042ad2f1e0086366d23985f4221c","tid":624885,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:40:59.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}